The paper deals with the problem of finding a shortest synchronizing sequence for a finite state automaton, which involves optimization and decision-making. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, such as Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Programming Languages (cs.PL).
